---
import DocLayout from "../../layouts/DocLayout.astro";
---

<DocLayout title="Policy Positions" description="AEGIS responses to emerging AI policy proposals and regulatory frameworks.">
  <h1>Policy Positions</h1>

  <p>
    The AEGIS Initiative responds to emerging policy proposals and regulatory
    frameworks that affect AI governance, safety, and security. As new
    legislation and executive actions shape the AI landscape, AEGIS provides
    technical analysis grounded in constitutional governance principles.
  </p>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>White House AI Framework Response</h2>
    <p class="placeholder">
      A formal response to the White House AI framework is currently in
      development. This document will analyze the framework through the lens
      of constitutional governance and provide recommendations for enforceable
      safety guarantees in autonomous AI systems.
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Congressional Engagement</h2>
    <p class="placeholder">
      Formal communications with members of Congress are forthcoming and will be
      published here with full text and response tracking.
    </p>
  </section>
</DocLayout>

<style>
  .placeholder {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-subtle);
  }
</style>
